%^BOLD%^-=%^YELLOW%^Storms Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Drawing upon the wild energy of nature, this domain creates magical versions of the storms for which it is named.

The storms domain contains the following spells:

Snowball, Lightning Touch, Sleet Storm, Ice Storm, Stormwinds, Sirocco, Acid Fog, Stormrage, Storm of Vengeance

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nimnavanon

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
